OL,3,CMPs to re-introduce 'Ella's law'
OL,4,Cpledging UK to have clean air by 2030
OL,6,FA cross-party group of MPs said they
OL,7,Fwill re-introduce a bill in the name
OL,8,Fof a nine-year-old schoolgirl who died
OL,9,Ffrom an asthma attack linked to air
OL,10,Fpollution.
OL,12,FDubbed "Ella's Law," the proposed
OL,13,Flegislation is named after Ella Adoo-
OL,14,FKissi-Debrah, who lived 82ft from the
OL,15,Fbusy South Circular Road in Lewisham
OL,16,Fand suffered a fatal asthma attack in
OL,17,FFebruary 2013.
