OL,3,CMPs to re-introduce 'Ella's law'
OL,4,Cpledging UK to have clean air by 2030
OL,6,FShe became the first person to have
OL,7,Fair pollution listed as a cause of
OL,8,Fdeath following a landmark inquest in
OL,9,F2020.
OL,11,FSian Berry, Green MP for Brighton
OL,12,FPavilion, will present the bill to the
OL,13,FHouse of Commons with a speech on
OL,14,FTuesday July 1, with the aim of making
OL,15,Fclean air a human right under UK law.
