OL,3,CMPs to re-introduce 'Ella's law'
OL,4,Cpledging UK to have clean air by 2030
OL,6,FIf passed, the bill would require the
OL,7,Fgovernment to achieve clean air
OL,8,Fthroughout England by January 1 2030,
OL,9,Fsetting out a pathway to bring the
OL,10,Fcountry in line with World Health
OL,11,FOrganisation air pollution guidelines.
OL,13,FShe has so far been backed by cross-
OL,14,Fparty Labour, Liberal Democrat, SNP
OL,15,Fand Independent MPs but hopes that
OL,16,Fmore will support the bill and it will
OL,17,Fbe picked up by the government in the
OL,18,Fnext King's Speech.
