OL,3,CMPs to re-introduce 'Ella's law'
OL,4,Cpledging UK to have clean air by 2030
OL,6,FElla's mother Rosamund Adoo Kissi-
OL,7,FDebrah has long campaigned for the
OL,8,Fgovernment to introduce stricter air
OL,9,Fpollution limits since her daughter
OL,10,Fdied.
OL,12,FIn 2022, a similar version of Ella's
OL,13,Flaw was steered through the House of
OL,14,FLords by Green Party peer Baroness
OL,15,FJones of Moulsecoomb.
OL,17,FIt was later sponsored by Caroline
OL,18,FLucas MP in the Commons until
OL,19,FParliament was dissolved for the 2024
OL,20,Fgeneral election.
