OL,3,CMPs to re-introduce 'Ella's law'
OL,4,Cpledging UK to have clean air by 2030
OL,6,FMs Berry said: "Deaths like Ella's,
OL,7,Fand the millions of lives blighted by
OL,8,Fpreventable diseases caused by air
OL,9,Fpollution, can be a thing of the past
OL,10,Fif governments start taking the right
OL,11,Faction now."
OL,13,FShe added: "Finally passing Ella's Law
OL,14,Fwill save lives, as it will make sure
OL,15,Fwe get new targets, and the funding
OL,16,Ffor local areas to achieve them by
OL,17,Fcutting down on the many causes of
OL,18,Ftoxic pollution, from road traffic to
OL,19,Fwood burning."
