OL,3,CMPs to re-introduce 'Ella's law'
OL,4,Cpledging UK to have clean air by 2030
OL,6,F"I believe that everyone has a right
OL,7,Fto breathe clean air, no matter where
OL,8,Fthey live, the colour of their skin or
OL,9,Ftheir socio-economic background.
OL,11,F"We know that air pollution affects
OL,12,Fmost people in this country, but the
OL,13,Fharshest effects are felt by poorer
OL,14,Fand marginalised communities."
OL,16,FIn the UK, toxic air pollution is
OL,17,Festimated to cause between 29,000 and
OL,18,F43,000 premature deaths every year,
OL,19,Faccording to The Committee on the
OL,20,FMedical Effects of Air Pollution
